'''Irv''' is one of the doctors who was interviewed to replace Naomi.

==History==
Irv came in to interview for a job at [[Seaside Health and Wellness]]. When asked why he chose to become a doctor, he said that when he was in school, you had three choices: lawyer, doctor, or dentist.

[[Jake Reilly]] was ultimately hired for the position.

==Career==
He is a doctor.
